commit_message: run example notebook with three datasets

add version of tf-nightly module used for the analysis.

Notice, tf-nightly v2.0.x produce oscillatory behavior of discriminator loss function in model AAE1.
This anomalous behavior affects the clustering of the pbmc3k dataset. The pbmc10k dataset is not affected.
add routine to scan of parameters which determine cluster similarity
add computation of cluster similarity in Base class

reduce default batch size

enables training on 4 nodes with 2 GPUs each.
update option variables to avoid ambiguity in batch script

remove tf.enable_eager_execution()

Deprecated attribute with tf-nightly 2.1.0.dev20191015
add adata attribute to Base class

Merge branch 'tf.distribute'.

Major changes:

- model classes VAE, AAE1, and AAE2 written in tf.keras API
- added TensorFlow distribution strategy
- added a separate section for notbooks and run scripts
correct account of number of workers in MultiWorkerMirroredStrategy
add workers of cluster as input
add number of neighbors and PCA components in update_label method for better comparison with the ground truth
run example VAE model with large batch size

improve distribute strategy for adversarial autoencoder.

Correct encoder prediction inside train_step method.

add distrebuted startegy for AAE1 model.

Implementation is not efficient. Training very slow.

add module gast v0.2.2 in mandatory requiroments.
The latestet version of the package is not compatible with the current tf-1.14.0
add train_on_batch method to class AAE2
add 'Dataset' mode and 'TFRecord' mode in models AAE1-2

added examples new clusters generated with splatter

update conversion of h5ad files to TFRecord format

remove batch normalization in decoder and discriminators of all models

experimental tf.keras implementation of variational autoencoder (VAE2)
remove batch_normalization in decoder and discriminators of AAE5
add script to install Graphviz library on Ubuntu system
move reconstraction phase before regularization in all the 4 AAE models
move recontraction phase before regularization in all the 4 AAE models
